ns do not disqualify a broad closure.\n\nThe preponderance of admitted evidence supports that Iran initiated a major non-weather closure affecting commercial flights transiting, arriving in, and departing from a major Iranian airspace region (western Tehran FIR).\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c4d89b0b1a4546f586501c46","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The admitted NOTAMs A0796/26 (PX-R1) and A1015/26"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The admitted NOTAMs A0796/26 (PX-R1) and A1015/26","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-02-15","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782831278133,"responseId":"gen-1782831278-ndJMCMXlFJP08vBXQHNt","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-20260216"}},"message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have received the opportunity to vote. Let me review the key elements from the prompt:\n\n**Proposition:** By May 24, 2026, 11:59 PM ET, Iran initiated a major non-weather closure of its airspace within the meaning of the market rule.\n\n**Key evidence admitted:**\n- PX-1/DX-1: Market rule defining \"major closure\"\n- PX-2/DX-2: NOTAM A1015/26 (NOTAMR A1010/26) from Notamify - closes all airports in west part of Tehran FIR except listed airports (operational sunrise-sunset), suspends previous permissions, requires Iran CAA permission for civil IFR passenger flights. Period: 2026-05-23 18:21 to 2026-05-25 08:30 UTC\n- PX-3/DX-3: Abdi Media report corroborating A1010/26 restrictions\n- PX-4/DX-4: Siasat report corroborating the restrictions\n- PX-R1/DX-S1: NOTAM A0796/26 from Notamify - \"Tehran FIR resumed normal operation, while west part remains closed for 